{"tid":2034093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文憑試試題外洩案 蕭源被判監14個月","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T05:11:32.000Z","uid":48124,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a1963ce6c0af00022230571e889cec480f81c14c","tid":2034093,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"Testing testing 試咪1234<br />\n<br />\n【最新】文憑試試題外洩案 蕭源被判監14個月<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17029&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17029%26refer%3DShare&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=8e6cf56f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Furgentnews.jsp%3FtaskId%3D17029%26refer%3DShare&h=e580362b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/urgentnews.jsp?taskId=17029&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n現代教育前中文科補習名師蕭源，透過手機向兩名前口試主考員，取得中學文憑試保密試題的案件，蕭源和兩名前主考員早前被裁定兩項串謀公職人員行為失當罪成。<br />\n<br />\n代表蕭源的大律師表示，蕭源一直沒有否認洩密行為，背景報告指蕭源對行為感到後悔、最初沒有想過事件的嚴重性，已有好好反省，並呈上4封求情信，希望法官考慮以非即時監禁形式處理。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官提到，不接納、不相信背景報告所指，蕭源第一時間分享獲得的試題，是為了預備下一屆的文憑試。她重申，即使無法舉證有沒有任何學生在事件中得益，被告的行為仍然打擊文憑試的公正性、打擊制度的根本，並不能輕描淡寫。<br />\n<br />\n辯方回應指，以往口試的題目均會在完成考試後約15分鐘在網上被公開，蕭源只是希望提早將試題曝光，以此作為「噱頭」招徠更多學生，強調並非想協助應屆考生作弊，出現「感知上的不公」是他始料不及。裁判官指，即使被告是純粹為個人生意利益，但現時的效果是打擊文憑試的公正性。"},{"pid":"0e5951a0283b4a5537a161678a848223d3956c5f","tid":2034093,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"誇張咗啲 咩事"},{"pid":"15db71a281e392bf2df74838febb6810e398e17f","tid":2034093,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"男女老幼多富窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ff841f0ef55bf90f4837c34a5f1bf24eb3f2b2","tid":2034093,"uid":13013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"比比描舉 定引分數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fa47d8a2e6d36231febe745dca37c113cf56df","tid":2034093,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1887b3293851b6a919aeaee569bb2f6986c67f66","tid":2034093,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"永遠懷念檸檬茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1509991/org/04b192ac3bfa2bdbba6b1217e5d297f3.jpg/pxfMNWI9HaGIi6T9od78GIK1qw3VQIS5VXMQ0FVzENA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1509991%2Forg%2F04b192ac3bfa2bdbba6b1217e5d297f3.jpg%2FpxfMNWI9HaGIi6T9od78GIK1qw3VQIS5VXMQ0FVzENA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f57fc57e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"402d69d29918578aaaacaefced2411ac870c4e2a","tid":2034093,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c1c46a7fcfbe1694b511fbd8391d22a0790fdd","tid":2034093,"uid":1544,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1887b3293851b6a919aeaee569bb2f6986c67f66","tid":2034093,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"永遠懷念檸檬茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1509991/org/04b192ac3bfa2bdbba6b1217e5d297f3.jpg/pxfMNWI9HaGIi6T9od78GIK1qw3VQIS5VXMQ0FVzENA?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1509991%2Forg%2F04b192ac3bfa2bdbba6b1217e5d297f3.jpg%2FpxfMNWI9HaGIi6T9od78GIK1qw3VQIS5VXMQ0FVzENA%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f57fc57e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"發覺燒完個樣幾似屎來母"},{"pid":